---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 285
  - Title: Prajnâ-Pâramitâ
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=Doctrine and Method
  - 365
---
Even as one desirous of reaching a longed-for city requireth the eyes
for seeing the way and the feet for traversing the distance, so, also,
whosoever desireth to reach the City of Nirvana requireth the Eyes of
Wisdom and the Feet of Method.
